These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, satire, fantasy, drama
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, helicopter, subway, ship
1. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
2. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
3. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
5. the person driving the ship is between the person driving the helicopter and the person driving the subway##2
6. the person watching drama movies is the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | mystery     | fantasy | satire |
| Transport     | van     | subway | ship  | helicopter      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, electronic, disco, ambient
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, tram, subway, van
1. the fan of electronic is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
2. the person driving the van is on the far left or far right##3
3. the fan of ambient is on the left of the person driving the van##1
4. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
5. the fan of disco is on the far right##1
6. the person driving the airplane is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | soul | electronic    | ambient     | disco  |
| Transport     | airplane    | subway | tram | van |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, country, folk, hip-hop
4 different pets are kept: bird, mouse, goldfish, dog
1. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the fan of country##3
2. the fan of country is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
4. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the fan of trance##3
5. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | country   | folk   | trance  | hip-hop |
| Pet           | mouse | dog | goldfish | bird  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, drawing, rock-climbing, gardening
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, chinese, russian, pakistani
1. the pakistani is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the russian##2
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3
4. the russian is on the left or right of the pakistani##3
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
6. the spanish is on the right of the chinese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | drawing | woodworking | gardening | rock-climbing  |
| Nationality   | chinese  | spanish   | pakistani  | russian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, tea, milk, coffee
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, magic-tricks, cooking, sudoku
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3
4. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | sprite    | tea   | milk | coffee    |
| Hobby      | magic-tricks | puzzles | cooking       | sudoku |

