.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, milk, hot-chocolate, water
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, van, helicopter, skateboard
1. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is between the person driving the skateboard and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
3. the person driving the subway is between the person driving the helicopter and the person drinking mirinda##2
4. the person driving the skateboard is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | mirinda | hot-chocolate | water | milk |
| Transport   | van | subway  | helicopter    | skateboard  |

