1. the person driving the trike is on the right of the australian##1
2. the australian is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
4. the russian is between the dutch and the mexican##2
5. the person driving the taxi is the person driving the taxi##1
6. the person driving the taxi is between the person driving the quad-bike and the mexican##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2   |   3    |     4      |
| Nationality   | australian | mexican | russian | dutch     |
| Transport     | train | trike  | taxi   | quad-bike |

