.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, rock-climbing, chess, cooking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, satire, comedy, martial-arts
1. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person watching satire movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
4. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
6. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Hobby         | cooking | chess | skydiving | rock-climbing   |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | comedy | crime      | martial-arts |

