.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-9::.
4 different pets are kept: frog, goldfish, cat, hedgehog
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, handball, soccer, snowboarding
1. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the owner of the hedgehog##1
4. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
5. the owner of the frog is on the far left or far right##3
6. the owner of the goldfish is between the person who's sport is handball and the person who's sport is rowing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Pet     | frog | goldfish   | cat      | hedgehog      |
| Sport   | handball     | soccer | rowing | snowboarding |

