.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, baking, traveling, hiking
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, van, bus, bike
1. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
2. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person driving the van##1
3. the person driving the bike is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3
5. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
6. the person driving the bus is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby       | collecting | traveling | hiking    | baking      |
| Transport   | bus       | bike       | van | roller |

