.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-13::.
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, mexican, egyptian, french
4 different pets are kept: turtle, snake, dog, hedgehog
1. the mexican is on the far right##1
2. the italian is the italian##1
3. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle##3
4. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the mexican##3
5. the egyptian is on the left or right of the french##3
6. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the french##3
7. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Nationality   | italian | egyptian  | french | mexican |
| Pet           | dog     | hedgehog | turtle    | snake     |

